{
  "id": "RAW_830e0ea9",
  "title": "Flex 布局下文字省略不生效？原因其实很简单",
  "url": "https://juejin.cn/post/7557880524083249203",
  "date": "2025-10-07 20:31:41",
  "author": "序猿杂谈",
  "siteName": "掘金本周最热",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"article-viewer markdown-body result\">\n   <h2 data-id=\"heading-0\">概述</h2>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p9-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/8acb14e97d9443119e43be273d4224a2~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5bqP54y_5p2C6LCI:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1760500563&amp;x-signature=M5qvmfjn60hM6n9wwF3jsw9gJb8%3D\" alt=\"flex_layout_ellipsis.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>在开发中，我们常遇到这种布局：A、B、C 三段文本长度不固定，其中 A、C 占用空间较少，需要完整显示；而 B 是自适应区域，超出部分需省略显示。A 与 B 共享同一容器，该容器与 C 同级，容器应占据除 C 之外的所有剩余空间。HTML 结构如下：</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-html code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"html\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"wrap\"</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"infos\"</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span>Soccer<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"self\"</span>&gt;</span>Campeonato De Reserva De Primera Division C<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"live\"</span>&gt;</span>Live<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p>如果按照常规思路编写 CSS，比如：</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-css code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"css\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.wrap</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">display</span>: flex;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">align-items</span>: center;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">350px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">border</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span> dashed <span class=\"hljs-number\">#ccc</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">padding</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">4px</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">16px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">gap</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">16px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.infos</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"11\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">flex</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"12\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">display</span>: flex;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"13\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">gap</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">8px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"14\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">align-items</span>: center;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"15\">}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"16\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"17\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.self</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"18\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">flex</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"19\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">padding</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">4px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"20\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background-color</span>: silver;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"21\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">border-radius</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">6px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"22\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">overflow</span>: hidden;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"23\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">white-space</span>: nowrap;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"24\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">text-overflow</span>: ellipsis;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"25\">}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"26\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"27\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.live</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"28\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">padding</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">4px</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">16px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"29\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: cornflowerblue;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"30\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">border-radius</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">6px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"31\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: white;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"32\">  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">flex-shrink</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"33\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p>渲染效果往往会出现问题，示例如下：</p>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p9-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/06407cdfe96e4f0da230fcf3698e27d7~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5bqP54y_5p2C6LCI:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1760500563&amp;x-signature=5B0hKLJS50BSfHW1Ns7VoePc35Y%3D\" alt=\"flex_layout_wrong.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>可以看到，.self 被内容撑开，导致右侧 “Live” 按钮被挤出容器。</p>\n   <h2 data-id=\"heading-1\">异常分析</h2>\n   <p>问题的根源在于 <strong>Flex 子项的默认行为</strong>：</p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p>在 Flex 布局中，子元素的默认 min-width 是 auto，意味着它会根据内容宽度确定最小值，导致内容不会被压缩。</p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p>因此，当 .wrap 的空间不足时，.infos 会拒绝被压缩，从而让内部的 .self 也失去“省略”的机会。</p>\n   <p>要让 .self 的 text-overflow: ellipsis 生效，必须确保它在空间不足时可以被压缩。</p>\n   <p>解决方案也很简单：<strong>给 .infos 设置 min-width: 0 即可。</strong></p>\n   <p>这告诉浏览器，“.infos 可以比它内容更窄”，从而允许内部 .self 根据空间自动裁切。</p>\n   <h2 data-id=\"heading-2\">实现</h2>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-html code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"html\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">html</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">lang</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"zh-CN\"</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">head</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">meta</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">charset</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"UTF-8\"</span> /&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">meta</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"viewport\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">content</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"</span> /&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">title</span>&gt;</span>Flex 布局下文字省略不生效？原因其实很简单<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">title</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">style</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"css\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">      * {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">margin</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">padding</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"11\">      }</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"12\">      <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">body</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"13\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">100vw</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"14\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">height</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">100vh</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"15\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">display</span>: flex;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"16\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">justify-content</span>: center;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"17\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">align-items</span>: center;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"18\">      }</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"19\">      <span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.wrap</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"20\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">display</span>: flex;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"21\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">align-items</span>: center;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"22\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">350px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"23\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">border</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span> dashed <span class=\"hljs-number\">#ccc</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"24\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">padding</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">4px</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">16px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"25\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">gap</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">16px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"26\">      }</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"27\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"28\">      <span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.infos</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"29\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">flex</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"30\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">display</span>: flex;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"31\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">gap</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">8px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"32\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">align-items</span>: center;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"33\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">min-width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* ✅ 关键：允许内部文字被压缩 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"34\">      }</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"35\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"36\">      <span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.self</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"37\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">flex</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"38\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">padding</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">4px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"39\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background-color</span>: silver;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"40\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">border-radius</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">6px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"41\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">overflow</span>: hidden;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"42\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">white-space</span>: nowrap;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"43\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">text-overflow</span>: ellipsis;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"44\">      }</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"45\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"46\">      <span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.live</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"47\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">padding</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">4px</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">16px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"48\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: cornflowerblue;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"49\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">border-radius</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">6px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"50\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: white;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"51\">        <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">flex-shrink</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"52\">      }</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"53\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">style</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"54\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">head</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"55\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"56\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"wrap\"</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"57\">      <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"infos\"</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"58\">        <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span>Soccer<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"59\">        <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"self\"</span>&gt;</span>Campeonato De Reserva De Primera Division C<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"60\">      <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"61\">      <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"live\"</span>&gt;</span>Live<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"62\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"63\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"64\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre>\n   <h2 data-id=\"heading-3\">总结</h2>\n   <table>\n    <thead>\n     <tr>\n      <th><strong>层级</strong></th>\n      <th><strong>是否需要</strong> min-width: 0</th>\n      <th><strong>原因</strong></th>\n     </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n     <tr>\n      <td>.wrap</td>\n      <td>❌</td>\n      <td>最外层容器，无需压缩</td>\n     </tr>\n     <tr>\n      <td>.infos</td>\n      <td>✅</td>\n      <td>是 .wrap 的 flex 子项，默认 min-width: auto 会阻止内部压缩</td>\n     </tr>\n     <tr>\n      <td>.self</td>\n      <td>❌</td>\n      <td>父层已允许压缩，无需重复设置</td>\n     </tr>\n    </tbody>\n   </table>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p>结论：在 Flex 布局中，当内部文字的省略不生效时，<strong>优先检查文字外层的容器</strong> 是否设置了 min-width: 0。大多数情况下，只需在容器层加上这一行，就能彻底解决问题。</p>\n   </blockquote>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章详细解析了 Flex 布局下文字省略失效的常见问题，并提供了设置`min-width: 0`的简洁有效解决方案。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章详细解析了 Flex 布局下文字省略失效的常见问题，并提供了设置`min-width: 0`的简洁有效解决方案。",
  "summary": "文章深入探讨了前端开发中 Flex 布局下`text-overflow: ellipsis`不生效的常见痛点。通过一个典型的 A-B-C 三段文本布局案例，作者首先展示了问题现象：中间自适应文本区域在超出时未能正确省略，导致布局溢出。随后，文章分析了根本原因在于 Flex 子项的默认`min-width`是`auto`，这使得子元素会根据内容宽度确定最小值，从而阻止其被压缩。解决方案是给需要收缩的 Flex 子项（即包含省略文本的容器）的直接 Flex 父容器设置`min-width: 0`，以此允许其根据可用空间进行收缩。文章提供了完整的 HTML 和 CSS 代码示例，并用表格清晰总结了何时需要设置`min-width: 0`，极具实践指导意义。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Flex 布局中`text-overflow: ellipsis`失效是常见问题",
      "explanation": "当使用 Flex 布局时，即使设置了文本省略属性，文本内容也可能因为父容器的限制而无法正确省略，导致布局溢出。"
    },
    {
      "point": "问题根源在于 Flex 子项的默认`min-width: auto`",
      "explanation": "Flex 子项默认会根据内容宽度确定最小尺寸，阻止其在空间不足时被压缩，从而导致内部文本无法省略。"
    },
    {
      "point": "通过设置父容器`min-width: 0`可解决文本省略问题",
      "explanation": "给包含省略文本的 Flex 父项设置`min-width: 0`，允许其在空间不足时收缩，从而使内部文本能够正确应用省略效果。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "在 Flex 布局中，子元素的默认 min-width 是 auto，意味着它会根据内容宽度确定最小值，导致内容不会被压缩。",
    "要让 .self 的 text-overflow: ellipsis 生效，必须确保它在空间不足时可以被压缩。",
